I need to identify the capital contributed by shareholders in exchange for shares, both the initial and final values.

Looking at the balance sheet, I can find the line item "Paid-in Capital" which represents capital contributed by shareholders in exchange for shares.

From the balance sheet:
- Initial value of Paid-in Capital: 13000000.00 on 2023-12-31
- End value of Paid-in Capital: 13000000.00 on 2024-02-05

This shows that the paid-in capital remained unchanged during this period, meaning there were no additional capital contributions from shareholders.

```json
{"solution": {"initial value": "13000000.00", "end value": "13000000.00"}}
```
